09:28.930 --> 09:31.750
Nice neighborhood. Thanks for the tip.

09:33.410 --> 09:34.600
What's the good news?

09:34.640 --> 09:37.620
Massive coronary in Brentwood.

09:37.880 --> 09:43.120
