11:34.670 --> 11:36.620
I don't know.

11:36.650 --> 11:38.520
What's the matter?

11:38.530 --> 11:41.340
All this talk about
mothers, I'm not in the mood.

11:41.380 --> 11:43.180
I bet I could get you in the mood.

11:43.210 --> 11:46.490
Maybe, but it'd be a cheap manipulation.

11:48.320 --> 11:51.980
All right, but don't come rubbing up
against me in the middle of the night.

11:52.010 --> 11:53.380
I won't.

11:53.400 --> 11:56.590
- Fine. Good night.
- Good night.

