13:23.720 --> 13:25.860
but really, who had a good one?

13:25.910 --> 13:28.670
And isn't it time we forgive and forget?

13:28.680 --> 13:30.030
Where's this coming from?

13:30.070 --> 13:33.070
No, I'm just saying that
maybe our lives would be richer

13:33.110 --> 13:36.640
if we let go of this pointless
resentment toward our mother and,

13:36.650 --> 13:39.480
and just moved on with our lives.

13:39.510 --> 13:42.040
She got to you, didn't she?

13:42.050 --> 13:43.510
What are you talking about?

13:43.550 --> 13:46.640
What did she do? Pay off your car?

13:47.390 --> 13:50.400
Get that dead black tooth fixed?

13:50.710 --> 13:53.290
Oh, listen to yourself. Excuse
me. I have to go to work.

13:53.750 --> 13:56.260
- Hold it.
- What?

13:56.610 --> 13:59.080
- Your watch.
- What about it?

13:59.090 --> 14:02.170
It doesn't have Hamburglars
on the wristband.

14:04.600 --> 14:06.260
